the%20bottle%20you%20want%20with%20your%20contact%20information%20on%20this%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EOne%20new%20listing%20of%20an%20antique%20bottle%20will%20result%20in%20a%20two%20month%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20wish%20list%20listing.%20A%20new%20antique%20bottle%20Hunt%20Story%20or%20article%20will%20result%20in%20a%20six%20month%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20wish%20list%20listing.%20Each%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20collector%20who%20contributes%20content%20will%20be%20allowed%20one%20and%20only%20one%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20or%20old%20bottle%20on%20their%20wish%20list%20at%20any%20time.%20Any%20individual%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20can%20only%20be%20listed%20by%20one%20site%20contributor%20so%20get%20in%20now%20and%20lock%20up%20the%20one%20you%20want%20in%20case%20someone%20finds%20it%20and%20wants%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20today.%20When%20an%20antique%20bottle%20listing%20expires%20another%20collector%20may%20take%20over%20that%20listing%20by%20contributing%20content.%20The%20expiration's%20I%20have%20set%20on%20these%20listings%20are%20intended%20to%20encourage%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20collectors%20to%20contribute%20new%20content%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20their%20wish%20list%20bottle%20on%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3ESome%20major%20previous%20and%20ongoing%20contributors%20to%20this%20Wisconsin%20antique%20bottle%20site%20have%20a%20perpetual%20right%20to%20have%20a%20bottle%20on%20the%20wish%20list.%20This%20site%20generates%20a%20lot%20of%20antique%20bottle%20traffic%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20your%20chance%20to%20contribute%20and%20maybe%2C%20if%20you%20are%20lucky%20and%20the%20stars%20all%20line%20up%20just%20right%2C%20the%20chance%20to%20achieve%20your%20Wisconsin%20or%20really%20any%20antique%20bottle%20collecting%20Holy%20Grail.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%22Mr%20bottles%20wish%20list%20bottle%20is%20the%20Milwaukee%20antique%20Blossoms%20Badger%20Ale%20bottle%22%20href%3D%